ZH: 我们家的客厅有一个漂亮的壁炉。
EN: Our living room has a beautiful fireplace.
ZH: 寒冷的冬天，壁炉是温暖的象征。
EN: In the cold winter, a fireplace is a symbol of warmth.
ZH: 壁炉旁边的沙发是放松的好地方。
EN: The sofa next to the fireplace is a great place to relax.
ZH: 在壁炉旁烤火让我感到宁静和安心。
EN: Sitting by the fireplace and roasting fire makes me feel peaceful and at ease.
ZH: 壁炉里的火光恍如仙境。
EN: The firelight in the fireplace is like a fairyland.
ZH: 我喜欢在壁炉旁边读书。
EN: I love reading by the fireplace.
ZH: 壁炉的火焰是如此迷人。
EN: The flames of the fireplace are so enchanting.
ZH: 壁炉的烟囱传来温暖的味道。
EN: The chimney of the fireplace emits a warm aroma.
ZH: 在壁炉旁边感觉自然而然地进入了冬季的氛围。
EN: Being next to the fireplace naturally immerses one in the atmosphere of winter.
ZH: 壁炉的炉子可以煎炒食物。
EN: The stovetop of the fireplace can be used to fry food.
ZH: 在壁炉旁边度过一个浪漫的夜晚是非常浪漫的。
EN: Spending a romantic evening by the fireplace is incredibly romantic.
ZH: 我喜欢坐在壁炉旁边喝杯热可可。
EN: I enjoy sitting by the fireplace and having a cup of hot cocoa.
ZH: 透过壁炉的火红色火光，我感到温馨。
EN: Through the fiery flames of the fireplace, I feel cozy.
ZH: 我把壁炉当作家里最温暖的地方之一。
EN: I consider the fireplace as one of the warmest spots in my house.
ZH: 冬日里的壁炉是温暖和欢乐的象征。
EN: The fireplace is a symbol of warmth and joy in winter.
ZH: 我喜欢围坐在壁炉旁开派对。
EN: I enjoy throwing parties and gathering around the fireplace.
ZH: 你觉得壁炉的设计怎么样？
EN: What do you think of the fireplace design?
ZH: 壁炉的砖石让人感到古舒适。
EN: The bricks of the fireplace give a nostalgic and comfortable feeling.
ZH: 我想在壁炉旁边放些蜡烛，气氛会更好。
EN: I want to place some candles next to the fireplace, it will create a better atmosphere.
